Subject: [Patch v7 01/12] [media] s5p-mfc: Rename IS_MFCV8 macro
Date: Wed, 24 Jan 2018 16:29:33 +0530
Message-id: <1516791584-7980-2-git-send-email-smitha.t@samsung.com>
In-reply-to: <1516791584-7980-1-git-send-email-smitha.t@samsung.com>
